summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1307, for the improvement of Fifth Avenue North, from Aloha Street to Prospect Street, and Prospect Street, from Fifth Avenue North to Seventh Avenue North, by constructing concrete walks, under Ordinance No. 14749 and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
